<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Verify Your RentEazy Account</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        padding: 40px;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #2d6cdf;
      }
      .otp-box {
        background: #2d6cdf;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 30px 0;
        text-align: center;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #888;
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to RentEazy!</h1>
    <p>Hi <strong><%= data.name %></strong>,</p>
    <p>Thank you for signing up on <strong>RentEazy</strong>. To verify your email address and activate your account, please use the OTP code below:</p>

    <div class="otp-box">
        <%= data.otp %>
    </div>

    <p>This OTP is valid for the next 10 minutes. If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>

    <p>Happy Renting,<br>The RentEazy Team</p>

    <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> RentEazy. All rights reserved.
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
